  <name>GTK LLM Chat</name>
  <summary>A GTK frontend for chatting with Large Language Models</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      GTK LLM Chat is a modern, user-friendly desktop application that provides 
      a graphical interface for interacting with various Large Language Models (LLMs).
    </p>
    <p>
      Features include:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Support for multiple LLM providers</li>
      <li>Conversation history management</li>
      <li>System tray integration</li>
      <li>Modern GTK4/Libadwaita interface</li>
      <li>Local conversation storage</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
